Xuan Yongnian's family, come get the patient.

852
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:40,640
Here, here, over here!

853
00:32:40,640 --> 00:32:41,840
Here, here, right here!

854
00:32:57,400 --> 00:32:59,760
How will you explain when he wakes up?

855
00:33:02,000 --> 00:33:03,000
Just stall for now.

856
00:33:03,480 --> 00:33:04,960
Buy as much time as I can.

857
00:33:05,760 --> 00:33:07,080
When I can't stall anymore,

858
00:33:07,760 --> 00:33:09,080
worst case, he beats me up.

859
00:33:10,040 --> 00:33:10,840
Who knows,

860
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:12,640
it might even do him some good.

861
00:33:15,360 --> 00:33:17,320
You've really got some nerve.

862
00:33:24,960 --> 00:33:25,760
And it's so much.

863
00:33:25,840 --> 00:33:27,520
I did a rough calculation.

864
00:33:28,000 --> 00:33:29,400
The orders placed so far,

865
00:33:29,640 --> 00:33:32,160
altogether come to about this much.

866
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:33,840
Five...

867
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:36,480
million.

868
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:42,160
That's nothing.

869
00:33:42,920 --> 00:33:44,360
If we sell everything,

870
00:33:45,160 --> 00:33:46,400
add another 1.5.

871
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:49,760
Mom.

872
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:52,400
Me,

873
00:33:52,840 --> 00:33:54,360
seeing you every day,

874
00:33:54,640 --> 00:33:56,200
scrimping and saving everywhere

875
00:33:56,400 --> 00:33:58,600
just to pay the workers,

876
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:00,000
it really breaks my heart.

877
00:34:01,520 --> 00:34:02,800
The reason I'm doing this

878
00:34:03,200 --> 00:34:05,560
is so you two won't worry so much.

879
00:34:06,240 --> 00:34:08,520
As long as you're not stressed

880
00:34:08,960 --> 00:34:10,000
about money,

881
00:34:10,320 --> 00:34:11,520
whatever the outcome,

882
00:34:11,520 --> 00:34:12,679
I can accept it.

883
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:15,600
Even if Dad beats me to death,

884
00:34:15,639 --> 00:34:16,560
I'd be happy.

885
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:20,239
I haven't loved you for nothing.

886
00:34:23,080 --> 00:34:24,000
That's right, Auntie.

887
00:34:24,520 --> 00:34:26,639
I'll help you talk to Uncle Xuan then.

888
00:34:26,679 --> 00:34:28,040
He'll definitely understand.

889
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:32,159
You clearly don't know my dad.

890
00:34:33,080 --> 00:34:33,920
All right.

891
00:34:34,920 --> 00:34:35,960
When he wakes up,

892
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:39,600
I'll help you hide it from him.

893
00:34:41,639 --> 00:34:43,600
But this beating,

894
00:34:43,679 --> 00:34:45,000
you won't escape it.

895
00:34:45,639 --> 00:34:46,920
Then while he's still out,

896
00:34:47,080 --> 00:34:48,560
let me deal with him first.

897
00:34:48,760 --> 00:34:49,639
What are you doing?

898
00:34:50,239 --> 00:34:50,840
What?

899
00:34:50,840 --> 00:34:51,600
No, I mean,

900
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:53,760
I've got a ton of things waiting for me.

901
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:54,840
While I have the time now,

902
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,840
let me clean him up, wipe him down.

903
00:35:00,280 --> 00:35:01,360
Let me do it, I'll do it.

904
00:35:01,400 --> 00:35:02,520
You chat with Auntie.

905
00:35:11,800 --> 00:35:13,280
He's about to give you a beating,

906
00:35:14,000 --> 00:35:15,560
and you're still wiping him down?

907
00:35:17,440 --> 00:35:18,360
I'm just afraid one day

908
00:35:19,520 --> 00:35:20,840
he won't be able to beat me anymore.

909
00:35:29,800 --> 00:35:30,600
Where are you going?

910
00:35:31,240 --> 00:35:32,160
Back to the town.

911
00:35:33,080 --> 00:35:33,800
If I remember correctly,

912
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:35,240
your home is in the county town, right?

913
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,280
Today's the weekend, too.

914
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:37,280
Aren't you going home to visit?

915
00:35:38,240 --> 00:35:39,440
I've still got work to do.

916
00:35:40,320 --> 00:35:41,720
It can wait a day or two.

917
00:35:42,000 --> 00:35:43,800
Here, send me the location.

918
00:35:43,800 --> 00:35:44,880
I'll take you back for a visit.

919
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:50,440
Xin Ran.

920
00:35:50,960 --> 00:35:52,200
Grab my gloves for me.

921
00:35:53,800 --> 00:35:54,800
Hello, Mr. Xin.

922
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:56,640
What's up?

923
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:58,680
Why?

924
00:36:03,800 --> 00:36:04,600
Well, in that case,

925
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:05,840
I won't hold back.

926
00:36:07,160 --> 00:36:08,760
Okay, got it.

927
00:36:09,040 --> 00:36:09,840
Bye-bye.

928
00:36:12,040 --> 00:36:12,920
Something come up?

929
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:14,600
Xin Ran said their chairman

930
00:36:14,600 --> 00:36:16,120
sent some VP Zhang

931
00:36:16,120 --> 00:36:17,520
insisting on delivering money to me.

932
00:36:17,800 --> 00:36:18,560
Oh, right, right, right.

933
00:36:18,560 --> 00:36:20,840
Hurry and call Chairman Xiao.

934
00:36:20,840 --> 00:36:21,880
Tell him I said

935
00:36:21,880 --> 00:36:23,520
to halt all sales.

936
00:36:23,520 --> 00:36:25,520
Dayazhai is buying up all the rest.

937
00:36:26,080 --> 00:36:27,960
Then why not just call him yourself?

938
00:36:28,120 --> 00:36:29,400
Dayazhai is paying so much,

939
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:30,920
how could I refuse?

940
00:36:31,200 --> 00:36:32,440
But I'd feel awkward

941
00:36:32,440 --> 00:36:33,880
talking to Chairman Xiao about it.

942
00:36:33,880 --> 00:36:35,760
So I have to ask you to step in.

943
00:36:38,680 --> 00:36:39,520
All right.

944
00:36:39,920 --> 00:36:41,480
Just do as I say. Get in.

945
00:36:44,280 --> 00:36:45,040
Hold on tight.

946
00:37:11,280 --> 00:37:12,880
Alright, sure.

947
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:15,960
I've arrived.

948
00:37:17,520 --> 00:37:18,320
Have a seat.

949
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:20,600
I'll hang up now.

950
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,160
You shouldn't have.

951
00:37:28,480 --> 00:37:29,240
Xiao Xuan.

952
00:37:29,920 --> 00:37:32,120
Let's cut to the chase.

953
00:37:32,680 --> 00:37:34,120
How much do you have left?

954
00:37:34,680 --> 00:37:36,720
I'll buy it all in one go.

955
00:37:38,920 --> 00:37:40,520
Give me a moment, let me check.

956
00:37:44,440 --> 00:37:45,040
Here.

957
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:47,200
What do you mean?

958
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:50,480
We don't even dare open our warehouse doors.

959
00:37:50,480 --> 00:37:51,640
Buyers picking up goods

960
00:37:51,640 --> 00:37:53,160
all have to wait outside the gate.

961
00:37:53,960 --> 00:37:54,800
So,

962
00:37:55,120 --> 00:37:56,680
don't ask me how much is left.

963
00:37:56,920 --> 00:37:57,800
The moment we open the doors,

964
00:37:58,600 --> 00:37:59,960
no amount would be enough for the rush.

965
00:38:02,880 --> 00:38:03,640
You...

966
00:38:04,240 --> 00:38:05,840
I'm... I'm Zhang.

967
00:38:05,840 --> 00:38:06,640
Vice President Zhang.

968
00:38:06,920 --> 00:38:08,960
Your second sentence just now, were you saying

969
00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:10,200
if I take it all at once,

970
00:38:10,200 --> 00:38:11,800
could you give me a discount?

971
00:38:13,000 --> 00:38:14,120
If you took it all at once,

972
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:15,320
these paper buyers

973
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:16,520
would break your legs.

974
00:38:18,240 --> 00:38:19,920
Actually, I came today

975
00:38:19,920 --> 00:38:21,560
on behalf of the Chairman.

976
00:38:22,600 --> 00:38:23,720
He was hoping

977
00:38:24,160 --> 00:38:26,320
we could buy up the entire lot.

978
00:38:32,520 --> 00:38:35,040
If buying it all isn't possible,

979
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:38,040
could you set aside a bit more for me?

980
00:38:38,960 --> 00:38:40,080
I understand.

981
00:38:40,320 --> 00:38:41,800
It's not easy for any of us.

982
00:38:41,920 --> 00:38:42,880
This time I came—

983
00:38:46,600 --> 00:38:47,400
Let me take this call.

984
00:38:50,280 --> 00:38:51,080
Hello?

985
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:52,600
What's going on?

986
00:38:56,160 --> 00:38:56,960
What?

987
00:38:58,960 --> 00:39:00,120
Are you serious?

988
00:39:11,480 --> 00:39:12,720
Alright, I got it, I got it.

989
00:39:13,880 --> 00:39:15,000
Wait for my update.

990
00:39:19,320 --> 00:39:20,360
The way things stand now,

991
00:39:20,680 --> 00:39:21,880
no matter how much I give you,

992
00:39:22,120 --> 00:39:23,440
I'll be offending Chairman Xiao.

993
00:39:25,440 --> 00:39:26,080
Well, well, well...

994
00:39:29,160 --> 00:39:31,600
Since I'm going to offend him anyway,

995
00:39:31,920 --> 00:39:32,920
I might as well

996
00:39:33,240 --> 00:39:34,560
offend him all the way.

997
00:39:35,640 --> 00:39:36,440
Bold move!

998
00:39:36,440 --> 00:39:37,800
I love doing business

999
00:39:37,800 --> 00:39:39,640
with bold young people like you.

1000
00:39:40,440 --> 00:39:41,240
Alright then.

1001
00:39:41,360 --> 00:39:43,000
I'll take the liberty

1002
00:39:43,000 --> 00:39:45,000
of giving you everything that's left.

1003
00:39:45,640 --> 00:39:47,520
At a 50% markup.

1004
00:39:50,680 --> 00:39:52,400
What does that mean, Vice President Zhang?

1005
00:39:52,880 --> 00:39:56,320
I need to discuss this with our Chairman.

1006
00:39:56,520 --> 00:39:57,560
Right, right, right.

1007
00:39:57,600 --> 00:39:58,600
Then hurry, hurry up.

1008
00:39:58,600 --> 00:39:59,600
Time waits for no one.

1009
00:39:59,600 --> 00:40:01,000
I'll go right now.

1010
00:40:01,080 --> 00:40:02,160
Quick, quick, go now.

1011
00:40:02,160 --> 00:40:03,880
I'll hurry right now.

1012
00:40:03,880 --> 00:40:04,400
Wait for me.

1013
00:40:04,400 --> 00:40:05,000
Hurry up!

1014
00:40:17,160 --> 00:40:18,360
Comrade Xuan Yu

1015
00:40:18,880 --> 00:40:21,120
What the hell are you up to?

1016
00:40:21,520 --> 00:40:22,600
You had Lin Yiran call me.

1017
00:40:22,600 --> 00:40:23,880
What's that supposed to mean?

1018
00:40:25,600 --> 00:40:27,040
Is Dayazhai really buying it all?

1019
00:40:27,880 --> 00:40:29,160
Don't worry if it's real or not.

1020
00:40:29,360 --> 00:40:30,520
Just keep playing along.

1021
00:40:30,760 --> 00:40:31,600
If someone wants to buy,

1022
00:40:32,120 --> 00:40:33,160
then raise the price.

1023
00:40:34,160 --> 00:40:36,640
What on earth are you scheming?

1024
00:40:36,680 --> 00:40:37,880
Taking advantage of the situation.

1025
00:40:38,720 --> 00:40:39,960
Taking advantage of the situation?

1026
00:40:40,360 --> 00:40:42,400
Is that one of the Thirty-Six Stratagems?

1027
00:40:43,120 --> 00:40:44,320
Well, listen up.

1028
00:40:44,680 --> 00:40:47,640
This is Uncle Xuan's thirty-seventh stratagem.

1029
00:40:48,880 --> 00:40:49,680
So, what do you think?

1030
00:40:50,160 --> 00:40:51,880
He was worth raising, wasn't he?

1031
00:40:52,080 --> 00:40:53,160
Not a bad deal, right?

1032
00:40:53,680 --> 00:40:55,760
He wipes you down,

1033
00:40:56,120 --> 00:40:58,160
and gets you chicken soup too.

1034
00:40:59,800 --> 00:41:00,760
Xuan Yu said

1035
00:41:02,160 --> 00:41:03,600
he asked a classmate,

1036
00:41:04,120 --> 00:41:05,360
who asked a friend,

1037
00:41:05,720 --> 00:41:07,320
just to find you this kind,

1038
00:41:07,320 --> 00:41:09,200
soup made from free-range old hens.

1039
00:41:10,040 --> 00:41:11,400
Here, have some.

1040
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:14,600
No, I don't want any.

1041
00:41:15,080 --> 00:41:17,400
You need it after surgery. Come on.

1042
00:41:21,360 --> 00:41:22,600
More money's come in.

1043
00:41:23,680 --> 00:41:25,800
Didn't you say the paper was all sold?

1044
00:41:25,920 --> 00:41:27,520
Xuan Yu said it was sold out.

1045
00:41:27,960 --> 00:41:30,040
This must be a delayed payment.

1046
00:41:31,160 --> 00:41:32,000
How much?

1047
00:41:33,520 --> 00:41:35,000
A few hundred, a few thousand here and there.

1048
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:46,320
My son is really something.

1049
00:41:48,040 --> 00:41:49,560
With these few hundred thousand,

1050
00:41:50,880 --> 00:41:53,440
the factory can catch its breath again.

1051
00:41:54,040 --> 00:41:55,000
That's right.

1052
00:42:15,720 --> 00:42:17,200
Mr. Xin, you're back.

1053
00:42:17,640 --> 00:42:19,840
You discussed something this important with Xuan Yu

1054
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:21,400
and you met at a coffee shop?

1055
00:42:21,400 --> 00:42:22,960
Well, I was actually trying to

1056
00:42:23,440 --> 00:42:25,000
save some money for you.

1057
00:42:25,320 --> 00:42:26,120
Vice President Zhang,

1058
00:42:26,160 --> 00:42:27,320
right now the whole of Taohua Town

1059
00:42:27,320 --> 00:42:28,800
knows we're buying up everything.

1060
00:42:28,800 --> 00:42:30,880
People are scrambling for the paper even more now.

1061
00:42:30,880 --> 00:42:32,040
The prices keep going higher and higher.

1062
00:42:32,280 --> 00:42:33,960
This morning, someone even came to our Dayazhai

1063
00:42:33,960 --> 00:42:35,520
wanting to order the out-of-print paper.

1064
00:42:35,600 --> 00:42:37,440
He said whatever price we agreed on,

1065
00:42:37,440 --> 00:42:38,720
he'd pay ten percent more.

1066
00:42:39,080 --> 00:42:41,320
See? Everyone's gone crazy.

1067
00:42:41,440 --> 00:42:42,680
It's a rare commodity.

1068
00:42:42,920 --> 00:42:44,000
Of course they'd go crazy.

1069
00:42:45,080 --> 00:42:45,920
I don't... I...

1070
00:42:46,400 --> 00:42:47,400
What do you want from me?

1071
00:42:47,560 --> 00:42:48,400
Well...

1072
00:42:48,400 --> 00:42:50,000
Because their price was too high,

1073
00:42:50,000 --> 00:42:52,120
I didn't dare take too large a share.

1074
00:42:52,600 --> 00:42:54,120
If the chairman asks about it,

1075
00:42:54,120 --> 00:42:54,560
you...

1076
00:42:56,160 --> 00:42:58,480
How much higher is it than the chairman expected?
